init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: As you watch yourself go through life this time around, your past lives begin to slip away.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Will it be the same as one of your previous lives?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Will you live in the same town?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Will your choice of partner seem as inexplicable as it did in a previous life?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are comforted by the thought that each life has led up to this one.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You remember the previous life in which your pet dog died.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Maybe one day you will even be able to love yourself.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This is a story in which there are many reincarnations.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This is the life you had always wanted but never allowed yourself to live.
